OL,7,FGovernment plans to boost prison
OL,8,Fcapacity could fall short by thousands
OL,9,Fof cell spaces within two years and
OL,10,Fcost the taxpayer billions of pounds
OL,11,Fmore than anticipated, Whitehall's
OL,12,Fspending watchdog has warned.
OL,14,FThe National Audit Office (NAO) said
OL,15,Fcurrent expansion plans are
OL,16,F"insufficient to meet future demand"
OL,17,Famid a projected shortage of 12,400
OL,18,Fprison places by the end of 2027, with
OL,19,Fcosts expected to be at least #4
OL,20,Fbillion higher than initially
OL,21,Festimated.
