OL,7,FThe watchdog also said the then
OL,8,Fgovernment's 2021 pledge to create an
OL,9,Fextra 20,000 cells spaces by building
OL,10,Fmore prisons, temporary wings and
OL,11,Frefurbishing existing cell blocks is
OL,12,Fnow not expected to be met until 2031
OL,13,F` around five years later than
OL,14,Fpromised.
OL,16,FAs of September, a third (6,518) of
OL,17,Fthe 20,000 had been made available,
OL,18,Faccording to the NAO.
