OL,7,FReasons behind delays include
OL,8,F"unrealistic timelines" and
OL,9,Foverestimating the ability to get
OL,10,Fplanning permission for three out of
OL,11,Fthe six new prisons due to be built.
OL,13,FThe plans are now expected to cost
OL,14,Fbetween #9.4 billion and #10.1 billion
OL,15,F` least #4.2 billion more than 2021
OL,16,Festimates amid a rise in construction
OL,17,Fprices, the report said.
