OL,7,FThe report ` which comes ahead of
OL,8,Ffresh prison population projections
OL,9,Fdue to be published by the MoJ on
OL,10,FThursday ` found the "crisis" was a
OL,11,F"consequence of previous governments'
OL,12,Ffailure to align criminal justice
OL,13,Fpolicies with funding for the prison
OL,14,Festate, leading to reactive solutions
OL,15,Fwhich represent poor value for money",
OL,16,Fadding: "Years of under-investment in
OL,17,Fmaintaining the prison estate put MoJ
OL,18,Fand HMPPS in a weak position to
OL,19,Frespond to these increases."
