OL,7,FThe current expansion plans are
OL,8,F"insufficient to meet projected future
OL,9,Fdemand", with the MoJ "relying" on
OL,10,Fmeasures like the sentencing review
OL,11,Fannounced in October to "reduce demand
OL,12,Ffor prison places and close the gap
OL,13,Fbetween demand and capacity" and
OL,14,F"address a projected shortage of
OL,15,F12,400 prison places by the end of
OL,16,F2027, should its central population
OL,17,Fprojection be realised", it said.
