OL,8,Fdepartment "does not have any
OL,9,Fcontingency plans to increase prison
OL,10,Fcapacity as it views it has limited
OL,11,Foptions left to do this".
OL,13,FPia Sinha, chief executive of the
OL,14,FPrison Reform Trust, described the
OL,15,Ffindings as "damning" and said they
