OL,7,FSince September the Government has
OL,8,Fbeen freeing thousands of inmates
OL,9,Fearly in a bid to cut jail
OL,10,Fovercrowding by temporarily reducing
OL,11,Fthe proportion of sentences which some
OL,12,Fprisoners must serve behind bars in
OL,13,FEngland and Wales from 50% to 40%.
OL,15,FBut prisons are still expected to
OL,16,Freach critical capacity again by July.
