OL,7,FMoJ figures show there were 86,059
OL,8,Fadult prisoners behind bars in England
OL,9,Fand Wales on Monday, slightly higher
OL,10,Fthan the 86,038 recorded at the
OL,11,Fbeginning of last week.
OL,13,FThe so-called operational capacity for
OL,14,FEnglish and Welsh men and women's
OL,15,Fprisons is 88,852, indicating there is
OL,16,Fnow cell space for 2,793 criminals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
