OL,7,FHead of the NAO Gareth Davies said:
OL,8,F"The Government must learn lessons
OL,9,Ffrom the current prison capacity
OL,10,Fcrisis to ensure the long-term
OL,11,Fresilience and cost effectiveness of
OL,12,Fthe prison estate."
OL,14,FPrisons minister Lord Timpson said:
OL,15,F"This report lays bare the litany of
OL,16,Ffailures which brought our prison
OL,17,Fsystem to the brink. This not only
OL,18,Frisked public safety but added
OL,19,Fbillions in extra costs to taxpayers.
